<h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
<p>Hello <%= @user.name || "there" %>,</p>
<p>
We received a request to reset the password for your <%= @operator.name %> account linked to <%= @user.email %>.
</p>
<p>
To reset your password, please click the link below:<br>
<% if @reset_token.present? %>
  <% reset_url = edit_password_reset_url(@reset_token, email: @user.email, subdomain: @operator.subdomain) %>
  <%= link_to reset_url, reset_url %>
<% else %>
  <em>There was an issue generating your password reset link. Please try requesting a new password reset.</em>
<% end %>
</p>
<p>
If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. This link will expire in two hours for your security.
</p>
<p>
Thank you<br>
